    &lt;/tr&gt;
  &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Just as the same metal disc, which was stained by dust before, shines brilliantly when cleaned, so the embodied being, seeing the truth of Ātman, realizes oneness, attains the goal, and becomes sorrowless. (2.14)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;एको हि रुद्रो न द्वितीयाय तस्थुर्य &lt;br /&gt;
इमाँल्लोकानीशत ईशनीभिः ।&lt;br /&gt;
प्रत्यङ् जनास्तिष्ठति सञ्चुकोचान्तकाले &lt;br /&gt;
संसृज्य विश्वा भुवनानि गोपाः ॥३-२॥&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;table class=&quot;table-customised&quot;&gt;
  &lt;thead&gt;
    &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;th style=&quot;text-align: center&quot;&gt;Sanskrit Word&lt;/th&gt;
